steps.name: User should verify success message after login "Welcome Bipin"
User search hotel "Andhra Pradesh","Tirupati","Deluxe","18 July 2026","28 July 2026","1-One","1-One" and "1"
User should verify after search hotel success message "Select Hotel"
User scrolls down, save the first hotel name and hotel price
User select the first hotel and click ok to proceed to next page
User should verify after select success message "Book Hotel"
User scroll down and  add Guest Details "Mr.","Arun","Kumar","1236549873" and "test@gmail.com"
User add GST Details "9043592058","Greens Tech OMR Branch" and "Thoraipakkam"
User add Special Request "Valet parking needed"
User click credit/Debit/ATM Card and click card type as debit card and enter the payment details
User should verify after hotel booking success message "Booking is Confirmed" and save the order ID
User should verify same selected Hotel is booked or not
User quit native app
User is on the OMR Branch hotel web application
User enter "rookie.deepu07@gmail.com" and "Deepakumar@2003" in chrome page
User should verify success message after login "Welcome Bipin"
User go to my account page
User search the Order ID
User should verify same booked Order ID is present or not
User should verify same booked Hotel Name is present or not
User should verify same booked Hotel Price is present or not
User edit the Check-in Date "<Modify Date>"
User should verify after modify check-in date success message "Booking updated successfully"
User click on Cancel the order ID
User should verify after cancel booking success message "Your booking cancelled successfully"
